---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <div class="flip-title" id="flipTitle">
        <div class="flip-title-inner">
          <div class="flip-title-front">Menil Vuković</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Engineer, CEO, writer, and father. Building digital products at
        <a href="https://pearshadow.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pear Shadow</a>.
        Transforming ambitious ideas into reliable software.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="/about/" class="btn btn-primary">About Me</a>
      <a href="/blog/" class="btn btn-secondary">Read Blog</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-4">
      <article class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">Engineering</h2>
        <p class="card-meta"><span style="color: var(--accent);">15+</span> years</p>
        <p class="card-description">
          Android, wearables, fintech, and e-commerce. From startups to enterprises like
          Philips, Mayo Clinic, and Raiffeisen Bank.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">Leadership</h2>
        <p class="card-meta">CEO<span style="color: var(--accent);"> @</span>Pear Shadow</p>
        <p class="card-description">
          Leading a team of engineers and designers building scalable software solutions
          for clients worldwide.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">Writing</h2>
        <p class="card-meta">Technical <span style="color: var(--accent);"> & </span> Essays</p>
        <p class="card-description">
          Sharing thoughts on software engineering, venture building, and the intersection
          of technology and art.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">Plays Dota</h2>
        <p class="card-meta">Since <span style="color: var(--accent);">2006</span></p>
        <p class="card-description">
          Thinks he's ancient rank. Believes Invoker is the ultimate test of mechanical skill and
          game sense. Blames teammates for losses.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: var(--space-16);">
  <div class="container container-narrow">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">Recent Writing</h2>

    <ul class="post-list">
      {%- for post in collections.posts | limit(3) -%}
      <li class="post-item">
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-link">
          <h3 class="post-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          <time class="post-date" datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
        </a>
      </li>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </ul>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: var(--space-8);">
      <a href="/blog/" class="btn btn-secondary">View All Posts</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
